<i>noun</i>: 악화 [아콰], 격화 [겨콰], 가중 [가중] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>악화 [아콰]</dt><br>
<dd>1. aggravation; worsening</dd><br>
<dd>일이나 상황이 나쁜 방향으로 나아감.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which an incident or situation proceed in a wrong direction.</dd><br>
<dd>2. exacerbation; worsening</dd><br>
<dd>병의 증세가 나빠짐.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which the symptoms of a disease grow worse.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>격화 [겨콰]</dt><br>
<dd>intensification; aggravation</dd><br>
<dd>감정이나 행동 등이 지나치게 급하고 거세짐.</dd><br>
<dd>The state in which an emotion or behavior becomes overly hasty and tough.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>가중 [가중]</dt><br>
<dd>1. aggravation; increase</dd><br>
<dd>책임이나 부담 등이 더 무겁고 커지는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>A responsibility, burden, etc., becoming heavier or bigger.</dd><br>
<dd>2. being additional; being aggravated</dd><br>
<dd>형벌이 더 무거워지는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>A penalty or punishment becoming heavier.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>